{"tid":2389843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：英方以人權問題容許港人移居　若無學歷技能「等於難民」","createTime":"2021-02-01T07:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T02:21:13.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e36a763520a827e61bd5a2d95b5645bc7f4236d4","tid":2389843,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"英國 1 月 31 日開放 BN(O) 簽證申請，中央政府跟港府隨即反制，不再視 BN(O) 是旅行證件。行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀今早（1 日）在商台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》表示，相信反制措施「冇咩實質作用」，但可以作為向英方的「警示」，如果英方再採取進一步行動，有大量港人移民，中方可進一步反制。葉劉淑儀又表示，今次英國是開拓了「特殊渠道」讓港人到英國生活，但是部分人未必能夠融入當地文化，「你都係俾人歧視」，或成為「二等公民」；又指部分人可能全無學歷、技能，純粹因為英國認為香港有人權問題而獲准抵英，「咁佢哋去到其實咪即係等於難民。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%85-%E8%8B%A5%E7%84%A1%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD-%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91/?fbclid=IwAR2556wtecgeraJMLuFiIOu57_Di7Q5hMMLNcavIiqkk9CBww_e2cEdpH6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B1%2585-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%2583%25BD-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2596%25BC%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2556wtecgeraJMLuFiIOu57_Di7Q5hMMLNcavIiqkk9CBww_e2cEdpH6c&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=ccc2567e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B1%2585-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2